    "开启后，节假日自动跳过闹钟，补班日自动恢复响铃。也可以在日历中手动覆盖某天的响铃状态。" : {
      "extractionState" : "stale",
      "localizations" : {
        "en" : {
          "stringUnit" : {
            "state" : "translated",
            "value" : "When enabled, alarms are automatically skipped on holidays and restored on makeup workdays. You can also manually override the ring status for any day in the calendar."
          }
        },
        "zh-Hans" : {
          "stringUnit" : {
            "state" : "translated",
            "value" : "开启后，节假日自动跳过闹钟，补班日自动恢复响铃。也可以在日历中手动覆盖某天的响铃状态。"
          }
        },
        "zh-Hant" : {
          "stringUnit" : {
            "state" : "translated",
            "value" : "開啟後，節假日自動跳過鬧鐘，補班日自動恢復響鈴。也可以在日曆中手動覆蓋某天的響鈴狀態。"
          }
        }
      }
    },
    "开启开关可手动覆盖该天的闹钟响铃状态，优先级高于自动规则。" : {
      "extractionState" : "stale",
      "localizations" : {
        "en" : {
          "stringUnit" : {
            "state" : "translated",
            "value" : "Toggle to manually override the alarm status for this day. Manual overrides take priority over automatic rules."
          }
        },
        "zh-Hans" : {
          "stringUnit" : {
            "state" : "translated",
            "value" : "开启开关可手动覆盖该天的闹钟响铃状态，优先级高于自动规则。"
          }
        },
        "zh-Hant" : {
          "stringUnit" : {
            "state" : "translated",
            "value" : "開啟開關可手動覆蓋該天的鬧鐘響鈴狀態，優先級高於自動規則。"
          }
        }
      }
    },
